tem js-pageAnimeBtn\" href=\"../careerimage\">CAREER IMAGE</a></li>\n            <li class=\"c-nav__item c-nav__item--entry h-margin--sp-t80\">\n              <div class=\"c-nav__item-wrap js-navItem\">\n                <div class=\"c-btn--spin c-btn--box h-sp\"><a class=\"noline js-pageAnimeBtn\" href=\"../entry\"><span class=\"c-btn__inner\"><span class=\"c-btn__txt\" data-text=\"ENTRY\">ENTRY</span></span>\n                    <div class=\"c-arrow\">\n                      <div class=\"c-arrow__line\"></div>\n                    </div></a></div>\n              </div>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"c-nav__item c-nav__item--blank h-margin--t56 h-margin--sp-t38\"><a class=\"js-navItem\" href=\"https://goodlifes.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">CORPORATE SITE <i class=\"c-text--icon-win\"></i></a></li>\n            <li class=\"c-nav__item c-nav__item--blank\"><a class=\"js-navItem\" href=\"https://smarg.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">SMARG BRAND SITE <i class=\"c-text--icon-win\"></i></a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </nav>\n      <!-- /nav-->\n      <!-- main-->\n      <div class=\"l-main\">\n        <section class=\"c-visual peple\">\n          <div class=\"c-visual__fv\"></div>\n          <div class=\"c-visual__content peple__content people__block people__block--01\">\n            <div class=\"c-skew peple__block\">\n              <div class=\"c-skew__bg\"></div>\n              <div class=\"c-skew__content js-fadein__box\">\n                <div class=\"l-inner--1046\">\n                  <div class=\"c-visual__headbox\">\n                    <div class=\"c-visual__copy js-fadein__itemTweenMove js-fadein__itemTweenMove--left\"><img src=\"../assets/images/people/visual_copy.png\"/></div>\n                    <div class=\"people__headbox\">\n                      <h2 class=\"c-visual__head js-fadein__wrapper\"><span class=\"js-fadein__item\">PEOPLE</span></h2>\n                      <p class=\"c-sec__desc peple__desc js-fadein__itemTween\">満足したら、そこで成長は止まる。<br/>誰かと比べるでもなく、自分がこれと思う目標に向かって進む。そうすることで、自分にしかたどり着けない景色は見えてくる。</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"l-inner\">\n                  <ul class=\"people__list\"> \n                    <li class=\"people__item c-btn--spin js-fadein__box\"><a class=\"js-pageAnimeBtn\" href=\"../people/03\">\n                        <div class=\"people__num\"><span class=\"c-btn__inner js-fadein__alpha\"><span class=\"c-btn__txt\" data-text=\"Corporate Dept\">Corporate<br>Dept</span></span></div>\n                        <div class=\"people__img js-fadein__clipPath--bottom-top\"> <img class=\"is-bw\" src=\"../assets/images/people/item03.png\"/><img class=\"is-color\" src=\"../assets/images/people/item03_color.png\"/></div>\n                        <div class=\"people__txt js-fadein__alpha\">\n                          <p class=\"people__copy\">不動産の可能性を、<br class=\"h-pc\">もっと多くの人に。</p>\n                          <p class=\"people__name\">柳田 麻衣</p>\n                          <p class=\"people__info\">2022年入社 / 静岡大学人文社会科学部<br>Corporate Dept</p>\n                        </div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"people__item c-btn--spin js-fadein__box\"><a class=\"js-pageAnimeBtn\" href=\"../people/04\">\n                        <div class=\"people__num\"><span class=\"c-btn__inner js-fadein__alpha\"><span class=\"c-btn__txt\" data-text=\"Buyer Dept\">Buyer<br>Dept</span></span></div>\n                        <div class=\"people__img js-fadein__clipPath--bottom-top\"> <img class=\"is-bw\" src=\"../assets/images/people/item04.png\"/><img class=\"is-color\" src=\"../assets/images/people/item04_color.png\"/></div>\n                        <div class=\"people__txt js-fadein__alpha\">\n                          <p class=\"people__copy\">自分の理想も、周りの理想も、体現する。</p>\n                          <p class=\"people__name\">富士 直人</p>\n                          <p class=\"people__info\">2020年入社 / 亜細亜大学法学部<br>Buyer Dept</p>\n                        </div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"people__item c-btn--spin js-fadein__box\"><a class=\"js-pageAnimeBtn\" href=\"../people/05\">\n                        <div class=\"people__num\"><span class=\"c-btn__inner js-fadein__alpha\"><span class=\"c-btn__txt\" data-text=\"Sales Dept\">Sales<br>Dept</span></span></div>\n                        <div class=\"people__img js-fadein__clipPath--bottom-top\"> <img class=\"is-bw\" src=\"../assets/images/people/item05.png\"/><img class=\"is-color\" src=\"../assets/images/people/item05_color.png\"/></div>\n                        <div class=\"people__txt js-fadein__alpha\">\n                          <p class=\"people__copy\">自分の失敗を活かす、<br class=\"h-pc\">最強のチームを。</p>\n                          <p class=\"people__name\">鈴木 勇飛</p>\n                          <p class=\"people__info\">2019年入社 / 亜細亜大学国際関係学部<br>Sales Dept</p>\n                        </div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"people__item c-btn--spin js-fadein__box\"><a class=\"js-pageAnimeBtn\" href=\"../people/06\">\n                        <div class=\"people__num\"><span class=\"c-btn__inner js-fadein__alpha\"><span class=\"c-btn__txt\" data-text=\"Buyer Dept\">Buyer<br>Dept</span></span></div>\n                        <div class=\"people__img js-fadein__clipPath--bottom-top\"> <img class=\"is-bw\" src=\"../assets/images/people/item06.png\"/><img class=\"is-color\" src=\"../assets/images/people/item06_color.png\"/></div>\n                        <div class=\"people__txt js-fadein__alpha\">\n                          <p class=\"people__copy\">20代で、圧倒的な<br class=\"h-pc\">存在感のある人間に。 </p>\n                          <p class=\"people__name\">小峰 雄</p>\n                          <p class=\"people__info\">2021年入社 / 立命館大学経済学部<br>Buyer Dept</p>\n                        </div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"people__item c-btn--spin js-fadein__box\"><a class=\"js-pageAnimeBtn\" href=\"../people/07\">\n                        <div class=\"people__num\"><span class=\"c-btn__inner js-fadein__alpha\"><span class=\"c-btn__txt\" data-text=\"Sales Dept\">Sales<br>Dept</span></span></div>\n                        <div class=\"people__img js-fadein__clipPath--bottom-top\"> <img class=\"is-bw\" src=\"../assets/images/people/item07.png\"/><img class=\"is-color\" src=\"../assets/images/people/item07_color.png\"/></div>\n                        <div class=\"people__txt js-fadein__alpha\">\n                          <p class=\"people__copy\">誰よりも選ばれる<br class=\"h-pc\">営業に成り上がれ。</p>\n                          <p class=\"people__name\">井上 亮磨</p>\n                          <p class=\"people__info\">2022年入社 / 法政大学経営学部<br>Sales Dept</p>\n                        </div></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"people__item c-btn--spin js-fadein__box\"><a class=\"js-pageAnimeBtn\" href=\"../people/08\">\n                        <div class=\"people__num\"><span class=\"c-btn__inner js-fadein__alpha\"><span class=\"c-btn__txt\" data-text=\"Contract Dept\">Contract<br>Dept</span></span></div>\n                        <div class=\"people__img js-fadein__clipPath--bottom-top\"> <img class=\"is-bw\" src=\"../assets/images/people/item08.png\"/><img class=\"is-color\" src=\"../assets/images/people/item08_color.png\"/></div>\n                        <div class=\"people__txt js-fadein__alpha\">\n                          <p class=\"people__copy\">営業の成功を、<br class=\"h-pc\">線で支える。</p>\n                          <p class=\"people__name\">関 千尋</p>\n                          <p class=\"people__info\">2021年入社 / 慶應義塾大学文学部<br>Contract Dept</p>\n                        </div></a></li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n      </div>\n      <!-- /main-->\n      <!-- footer-->\n      <footer class=\"c-footer\" id=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"c-footer__content\">\n          <div class=\"c-footer__col\">\n            <div class=\"c-foot